 we have the activities of welcoming the lanterns and guessing the riddles. In addition, we have many activities for worshiping
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 God
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 in
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 January. The first is "An Tai Suei." There are 60 Tai Suei in
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a 60-year cycle. A different
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Tai Suei is the
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 guard for
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 each year
