 make Shin Ding Ban-new born baby boy rice cake and send it to the temple and their
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 relatives.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
In Hou Lung, we have
