Ching Ming Festival is the day to show filial obedience to your parents. It also has the meaning of feeling grateful and remembering our past. On that day, we have to hang 
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 (or, place)
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 paper
