July 7th is the birthday of Goddess Chi Niang. She is a Goddess
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 responsible for
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 children.
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 At the same time, she
