 simply in thanks
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 for the good health of their kids. Some children
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 will wear
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 picture of her
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 all year
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 and change
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 to
