 a bun and put a gold hairpin
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 through
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the bun. They will do this ceremony at home when coming to the right age. People used to ask for
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 blessing from Goddess Chi Niang, Goddess Guanyin, Goddess Ma Tzu and the God of Bed and wear a charm for health and safety. The charm
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 needed to be changed
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 every year
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 on the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 God\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s birthday and
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 taken
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 off
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 when
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 becoming an adult.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Talking about the wedding ceremony
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, in
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 traditional
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 thinking
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, men are the core members
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 of the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 family. Therefore, having
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a boy
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 has two kinds of meaning
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
:
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 one is hoping he could support the family after his parents grow old, and the other is to pass along the family name.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

