 they? Normally, we
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 needed
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 to check out her family history and her financial status. Also, her looks, morality and health would also be considered. However, modern people
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 are
