 a business arrangement with conditions.
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Some people would ask for money
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 gifts
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 when
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 marrying
