engagement and wedding now. Actually, nobody is following the old custom of six gifts anymore.  
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
"Ba Tzu" is also the thing you would want to know when getting married, but what is
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 "Ba Tzu"? It is the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 date, year and time of your birth
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
.
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 In
