 olden
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 times, people would put
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 bride\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s Ba Tzu on the God\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s table. If nothing
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 happened
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, and the girl
