 at a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 wedding should be a pair no matter
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 whether
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 cakes,
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 presents
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 or money. The
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 saying
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 says, "Good
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 things need
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a pair.  So this is also
