 and for the groom to do
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 "An Chuang." After
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 "An Chuang,"
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the bed should not be
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 left
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 empty. Greeting
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the bride,
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the groom should personally
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 go to
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 pick
