 should send chicken, clothes and
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 especially
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 pants to her daughter. After Shih Er Chau,
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the family
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 would worship
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 God
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 and send gifts such as sticky rice, egg wine and red eggs to
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 relatives.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
After Shih Er Chau, it is the time for fortune telling. When the fortune teller finds out the baby's Ba
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Tzu, he
