 will write a Current Year Book. And then, the ceremony of
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 full moon will be held. Guests would congratulate the mother
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 on
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the healthy baby and give gifts like chicken, baby clothes and
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 food
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
. Of course, there would be egg wine and sticky rice
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 as a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 treat. The name giving process is based on the baby\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s Ba Tzu
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 and deciding
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 what the baby
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 needs
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 in his/her life. After four months, there would be a ceremony called "Shou Yan"
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
--stopping
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 baby\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s drooling. In order to stop the drooling, Hau Ming Po would take some cookies to hang on his/her
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 neck, and
