 wipe off the
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 drool
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 to complete the ceremony. Later is the one-year ceremony. The
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 maternal grandmother
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 would put 12 things in a basket and let the child
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 grab one
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
. If the child grabs a pen, it means he/she will be good
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 at
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 studying. An abacus means
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 becoming
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a good salesman, a ruler means
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 becoming
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a good engineer, and food means never
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 having
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 to worry about food.
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 The twelve things all have
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 different
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 meanings.

}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Normally after
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 one-year ceremony, there was a ten-year ceremony in
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 ancient
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 times. And then
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the person
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 would get married around 20 years old. Next, it is
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 birthday
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 time. How to celebrate your birthday? Before
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 becoming
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 50 years old, all the birthdays are called
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 small
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 birthdays. You can only celebrate with your family
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 yearly. After 2 years of
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 marriage,
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 there will be a "New birthday" and this would be celebrated by your wife\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 family. In addition,
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 there is a "31." If the husband reaches 31 years old, the wife\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 family
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 would celebrate for him too. Both of
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 these
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 special birthdays would be held by the wife\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s family.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Someone
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 over
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 50 years old
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 is considered to be
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 60. The birthdays of 51, 61, 71, 81, 91 and 100 are "big birthdays."
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 The celebration of these
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 special occasions
