 a few moments
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 before death, with the head toward
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 outside and feet toward
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 inside. Men should be located on the left side and women on the right side. People would also put some coins on the hands of
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 deceased which
