 expresses the hope of
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 endless
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 good
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 fortune for the offspring.     
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Monks would be asked to write the date of death on a flag to represent
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 temporary
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 tomb. Also, a bowl of rice would be placed below the feet with an egg and a
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 chopstick
