}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, the family
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 would get down on their knees to say goodbye to the guests.  Before burying the body, the
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 grave
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 should be dug first and
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the dragon door opened
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 before covering the body with dirt. After finishing, a mound
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, which is called "Yuan Pen," needs
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 to be made
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 facing
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 in the right direction
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
After
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 digging
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 up the
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 spiritual remains
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 of the deceased,
