What is the story of Yi Ming
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Ye?
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 He
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 was involved in
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 two famous
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 events:
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 one is
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Lin Shuang Wen
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Incident
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 and
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the other
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 is
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Dai Chao Chun
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Incident.
