 events show
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 his courage
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 defending
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 his hometown. In the
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Lin
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Shuang Wen
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Incident
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
, over
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 one thousand
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Yi Ming
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 soldiers
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 fought
