 will
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 still worship him every day. Third,
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 at home by worshipers who have taken
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the flag which
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 represents
