 guard with green face and long tongue who stands beside the door.  Goddess Guanyin stands on his head to supervise whether the king of
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 ghosts is fair while distributing the food to other ghosts. There is a God of Mountain and a Bogung standing aside
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 him.
